title: The Eye Of Dobermans T1 For Devils Glory (Cero&Sosich) cbr
description:
Enlisted by obligation in the first word conflict,young soldier Arno Ixks saves the life,thanks to his exceptional instinct,of his warmongering corporal...the Gefreiter Adolf Hitler!
Twenty years later,Hitler did not forget his rescuer who became a renowned archaeologist.In his way of thanking him,he forces him to join Ahnenerbe,his sciientific division created to prove and legitimize the superiority of aryan race.Sent on the borders of Himalaya to investigate,Ixks will have to choose between saving himself from Hitler'claws and the truth!

enjoy
